name: They wept till they wept till
description:
Sure, a part of me still rested under a mound of dust that narrowed until it made a cocoon—pause again! Enter a narrow opening behind which... an itch resumed, unfolded from an invisible yellow spring whose springiness attested to all the other organs & & He was asked what he'd say to his past self if he somehow had a chance to pull down a curtain separating the two. He said, Nothing I wouldn't have said already, came out diplomatic as anything because it could only mean the wrong thing to the wrong folks, meant something else all together to those other folks!

A website. Made with CSS and GPT-3
